{"tid":1064079,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得「義工」已經變哂質？","createTime":"2019-03-16T09:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T06:25:40.000Z","uid":31076,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ff4dd9b4e9e7c4850147a39cbbf578c8ede11a","tid":1064079,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"先講下義工，本身做嘅範疇就係非牟利性質，好似幫明哥派下飯畀露宿者、探下獨居老人之類。唔好理大家係咪覺得有意義，但至少做嗰個自己係發自真心想做<br />\n<br />\n可惜而家個風氣，變咗係機構想節省成本請廉價勞工、做嘅人又只係想作為入行嘅踏腳石<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，藝術行業，大學生想入行咪報下Gallery、拍賣行Intern ，連啲車馬費飯錢intern 都唔夠人爭嘅咪唯有做義工起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請廉價勞工唔好聽，請義工就即刻變得有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前就連吳x坤開演唱會都可以請義工<br />\n<br />\n「人必自侮，然後人侮之」，無良僱主最低工資都唔駛畀、Peak season 想cut cost 請2個intern / 多個義工當一個長工洗，其實都係班自貶身價嘅大學生縱出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到最後，你會發現：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">寫落CV 真係有用嘅「經驗」都係會提供合理人工嘅Intern</span> e.g. 政府Intern"},{"pid":"b09be9b24c6309978630fbaeca0a366034c8fbc1","tid":1064079,"uid":136776,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"義工溝女王在此"},{"pid":"25c5aa793cdbac160996e9e5c00064609346eab0","tid":1064079,"uid":223328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b09be9b24c6309978630fbaeca0a366034c8fbc1","tid":1064079,"uid":136776,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"義工溝女王在此"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"你慢慢溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做義工緊係直接食女"},{"pid":"615afeed4e36e5aae4ac4f2ee19b1906dff43884","tid":1064079,"uid":31076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b09be9b24c6309978630fbaeca0a366034c8fbc1","tid":1064079,"uid":136776,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score"